- sy = Schoolyear.current_schoolyear.first
#left{:style => "width:49%; float: left"}
  #header.center{:style => "width: 40%; margin: 0 auto 30px;"}
    %a= pdf_image_tag '/images/upislogo.JPG', :style => "width: 85px; float: right;"
    University of the Philippines
    %br
    College of Education
    %br
    %span.capslock U.P. Integrated School
    %br
    Diliman, Quezon City

  .center.capslock
    %h4 Report Card
    %h4= "A.Y. #{sy.name}"

  #student_details.capslock
    %h3= @student.fullname
    %h3= @student.section(sy.id).fullname

  %h3.capslock.center Academic Performance
  %table.center{:id => "year-#{sy.id}", :style=>"margin: 30px 20px;"}
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Subject
        %th Q1
        %th Q2
        %th Q3
        %th Q4
        %th Average
        %th Final
        %th
          Completion
          %br
          Grade
        %th
          Credits
          %br
          Earned
    %tbody
      - @student.courses_year(sy.id).each do |c|
        %tr
          %td= c.subject.name
          - if !c.yearlong && c.sem == 2
            %td -
            %td -
          - @student.course_grades(c.id).each do |g|
            - if c.subject.is_pe?
              - if pe(g.value) == 'F'
                %td.emphasize= pe(g.value)
              - else
                %td= pe(g.value)
            - elsif !g.value.nil? && g.value < 50
              %td.emphasize= g.value
            - else
              %td= g.value
          - if !c.yearlong && c.sem == 1
            %td -
            %td -
          - if @student.course_has_blank(c.id)
            %td
            %td
          - else
            %td= c.student_average(@student.id)
            %td
              = @final = c.student_final(@student.id)
            %td
              - if @final == 4.0
                - @removal = @student.course_removed(c)
                = @removal.value
            %td= c.subject.units
      %tr
        %td{:colspan => 9}
          General Weighted Average:
          = @student.gwa_final_schoolyear(sy)

  %h3.capslock Transmutation Table
  #transmutation_table{ :style=>"width:50%; float:left;"}
    = render 'transmutation_table'
  %p{:style=>"float:right; width: 40%"}
    The final grade for any yearly subject is the transmuted grade to the 11-point system of the average of the points (in %)
    for the four grading periods. The final grade for any semestral subject is the transmuted grade to the 11-point system
    of the average of the points (in %) for two grading periods.
#right{:style => "width:48%; float: right"}
  %h3.capslock acts and behavior that show values
  %break
  %h3.capslock.center To parents or guardians
  %p.center
    This report card is issued periodically to apprise you of your child's academic performance, regularity in attendance and conduct.
    You may wish to discuss your child's progress' with his teachers and/or the guidance counselors durint their consultation hours.

